h2 Welcome to the REST Interface Policy Evaluator!

p We are currently researching the best practices to be used for the next generation of RESTful services. This "REST Interface Policy (RIP) Checker constitutes an investigative tool to gather feedback from the community at large.

p The vision is to create the user stories that encapsulate those best practices, and test them against user specified end points. The results ought to give an idea of how far such best practices may constitute an enforceable policy or standard for RESTful services.

